<div class="post-wrapper">
<h1 class="post-title"><a href="http://www.mama-knows.com/gardening-tips/how-to-grow-an-organic-tea-garden.html" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to How to Grow an Organic Tea Garden">How to Grow an Organic Tea Garden</a></h1>

<!-- article information div -->
<div class="articleinfo">Posted by Hanna Trafford in  <a href="http://www.mama-knows.com/gardening-tips" title="View all posts in Gardening" rel="category tag">Gardening</a> on  June 25, 2009 |  <a href="#postcomment" title="Leave a comment">one response</a><p><div style="float:left; padding-top:3px; padding-right:5px;margin-right: 10px;"> 	<a href="http://www.mama-knows.com/gardening-tips/how-to-grow-an-organic-tea-garden.html/print/" title="Print" rel="nofollow"><img class="WP-PrintIcon" src="http://www.mama-knows.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-print/images/printer_famfamfam.gif" alt="Print" title="Print" style="border: 0px;" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mama-knows.com/gardening-tips/how-to-grow-an-organic-tea-garden.html/print/" title="Print" rel="nofollow">Print</a>
